data.description: Updated home in middle of South Omaha. Home has 4 bedrooms (one expanded), 3 bathrooms, bonus/bar room, formal dining room, sunroom, pantry/mudroom, laundry on second floor. Lots of shopping and dining nearby. Close to Downtown and Little Italy. Sunroom in front only needs flooring. Some of the furniture can stay. Washer and dryer negotiable.
